config_examples         Examples of yaml configurations for database
                        connections
connect                 (Re-)Establish connections to databases
connection_info         Browse available connections
default_conn            Return the default connection
disconnect              Close all connections and remove them from the
                        connections cache
is_connected            Test whether a database is connected
live_connection         Return the named connection or NULL
prepare_sql             prepare queries and meta data for execution
read_sql                Read a sql file and return it's contents as a
                        tibble
runfiles                Read, prepare and execute .SQL files
runqueries              Execute a sequence of SQL queries
set_default_conn_name   Set/get the name of the default connection to
                        use
